      "title": "Experimental Data",
      "text": "<p/>Download the experimental data of the main manuscript at the following Open Science Framework  <a href=\"https://osf.io/k9w68/?view_only=62d2c8eb6a5c40e3896d6ef7c74131f2\" target=\"_blank\">link</a>.</p>",
